Tony Azito https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Tony_Azito 0 Tony Azito (July 18, 1948 – May 26, 1995) was an American eccentric dancer and character actor. He was best known for comedic and grotesque parts, which were accentuated by his hyperextended body.
